metadata.name: Gym A Club Mint Pass - Silver
metadata.description:
[OliveX Fitness Metaverse](https://twitter.com/OlivexFitness) is a P2E gamified fitness experience on the [Sandbox](https://opensea.io/collection/sandbox).

Silver Pass Holders enjoy whitelist minting access for its very first collection [Gym A Club](https://olivex.sandbox.game/) designed in collaboration with [Gym Aesthetics](https://twitter.com/GymAestheticsHQ). Avatars can be used to enter [Sandbox](https://www.sandbox.game/en/) and [OliveX Fitness World](https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=BzVPKdT1g4Y) to earn DOSE. Silver Passes are given to OG Holders within Discord, Gleam Competition Winners, Ambassador Campaigns, and other whitelisting activities.

Collection info and mint details [here](https://olivex.sandbox.game/).Ô∏è
